+- Architecture review is due after 002K by cadence (`slices_completed_since_architecture_review` reaches 4). 003A has already been sharpened to add only a protected paginated `GET /api/v1/audit-logs/` over the existing `identity.AuditLog` model, using `audit.audit_log.read` as the narrowest existing audit-read permission. 003B has been sharpened to reconcile the pre-existing tracer-owned `workflow_events` table before creating/owning any canonical workflow-event foundation.
 
